<h2>Corona News Updates Diff Comparison</h2>
<p>
This is a free service that will check the Israeli Health Ministry's website on Covid-19 (Corona Virus) and check for any updates every 12 hours. If there is an update it will send you a text message at the number you provide. 
</p>
<p>
SMS messages are sent using the <a href="https://developer.nexmo.com">Nexmo SMS API</a>.
</p>

<% flash.each do |type, msg| %>
  <div>
    <%= msg %>
  </div>
<% end %>

<%= form_with model: @recipient, url: "/recipient/new" do |f| %>
  <%= f.telephone_field :number %>
  <%= f.hidden_field :subscribed, value: true %>
  <%= f.submit "Add Number" %>
<% end %>